high_descs: Turn to the right and face the white table.
Pick the bread up from the table.
Put the bread in the fridge, shut the door and then open the door and take the bread out and shut the door.
Turn to the left and then left again to stand in front of the toaster on the counter.
Put the bread down on the counter.
anns.task_desc: Put chilled bread on the counter.

high_descs: Turn to the right and face the white table.
Pick up the loaf of bread from the front of the table.
Take the bread and turn around to go to the fridge.
Open the fridge and put the bread inside. Shut the door then open it again. Take the bread out and shut the door.
Carry the bread and turn left. Then turn left again to find the toaster on the counter.
Place the bread on the counter in front of the tea pot.
anns.task_desc: Chill a loaf of bread and place it on the counter.

high_descs: Pick up the loaf of bread on the edge of the table.
Turn around and walk to the fridge.
Put the bread in the fridge and close the door, wait a few seconds and then take the bread out of the fridge.
Turn to the left and walk forward to the sink, then turn left and walk to the counter.
Place the loaf of bread on the counter.
